    • BookingDetails

      public BookingDetails(String detailsId, String bookingId, String slotCode, String specialRequirements, boolean isWaitlisted, int waitlistPosition)
      Instantiates a new booking details with the specified parameters.
      Parameters:
      detailsId - the unique identifier for the booking details
      bookingId - the identifier of the associated booking
      slotCode - the code representing the gym slot
      specialRequirements - any specific requirements for the booking
      isWaitlisted - whether the booking is on the waitlist
      waitlistPosition - the position in the waitlist if applicable
